</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_174" id="87r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_174_r1l20">Mein <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> beuor . Hanns . Bernolt . Als du <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> vom Rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l21"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıben</expan> haſt von ırs <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Schürſtabs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / ſolt du <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l22">ſıe Jn <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒurede geſacʒt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / der hat <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> daʒ er niht wıſſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l23">daʒ er des deinen ıcht Jnnenhab . Dewcht dıch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ du <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l24">ıht <expan>ʒuſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hettſt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> well er <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l25">vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> hıe ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> . Hettſt du <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> guten ıht ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l26"><expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe macht du <expan>fürwende<ex>n</ex></expan> für dıe lantgerıcht darinn ſıe <expan>geleg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l27">ſınd . Vnd <expan>maine<ex>n</ex></expan> mein freẅnd vom Rate . du laſſeſt dıch des bıllıch be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l28">nügen . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l29">Nıclas Muffel ʒu der ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l30"><expan>burgmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="addressee"><p facs="#facs_174">
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l31">Dem <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l32"><expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Bernolt </ab>
</p>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_174" id="87r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab><app><note><q type="inline">Dem
        <expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Bernolt</q>Die Adresse dieses Briefs wurde im Original ausnahmsweise unter dem Brieftext eingetragen.</note></app></ab></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Mein <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bevor. Hanns Bernolt, als du
                                <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> vom rate
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schriben</expan> hast von irs
                            <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Schürstabs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc., solt du <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz sie in
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu rede gesaczt
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>; der hat
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t,</expan> daz er niht wiss, daz er des deinen
                        icht innenhab. Dewcht dich <expan>ab<ex>er,</ex></expan> daz du
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu im iht <expan>zu
                                sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hettst, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        well er <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> slewnigs
                            <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie zu
                        <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>. Hettst du <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> guten iht zu
                                <expan>spreche<ex>n,</ex></expan> die macht du
                                <expan>fürwende<ex>n</ex></expan> für die lantgericht, darinn sie
                                <expan>geleg<ex>en</ex></expan> sind. Und
                            <expan>maine<ex>n</ex></expan> mein frewnd vom rate, du lassest dich des
                        billich benügen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>.<lb/>Niclas Muffel,
                        zu der zeit <expan>burgmeist<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
